# Local Playbook — BetterCallClaude Italia

> Copy this file to the `.claude/` folder of your project (Claude Code) or to the shared folder (Cowork Desktop) and rename it to `bettercallclaude-italia.local.md`. Customize each section for your firm.

## Firm Profile

- **Name**: [Firm name]
- **Location**: [City]
- **Type**: Law firm
- **Main regions**: [e.g. Lombardia, Lazio]
- **Working languages**: IT, EN

## Standard Contractual Positions

- **Governing law**: Italian law
- **Jurisdiction**: Court of [city]
- **Liability cap**: Contract value
- **Penalty clause**: Art. 1382 CC — max [X]% of contract value
- **Express termination clause**: Art. 1456 CC — always included
- **NDA max duration**: 5 years
- **NDA preferred type**: Bilateral, reciprocal obligations
- **CISG**: Excluded per Art. 6 CISG

## Risk Thresholds

- **Value requiring mandatory human review**: > EUR [amount]
- **Clauses triggering escalation**:
  - Waiver of mandatory rights
  - Unlimited guarantees or uncapped indemnities
  - Derogation of Art. 1229 CC
  - Non-compete clauses (Art. 2125 CC)
  - Non-Italian jurisdiction
  - Foreign-seated arbitration

## Data Protection

- **Prevalent role**: Data controller
- **Applicable law**: GDPR + Italian Privacy Code (D.Lgs. 196/2003, mod. D.Lgs. 101/2018)
- **Extra-EU transfers**: Require adequate safeguards (Art. 46 GDPR)
- **DPO**: [Yes/No]

## Style and Format

- **Citation format**: Cass. civ., sez. [X], [date], n. [number]
- **Output format**: Markdown
- **Citation language**: Italian
- **Output folder**: bcc-output
- **Default length**: medium
